1. *Tražite* li strani jezik? (Are you looking for a foreign language?)
2. Oni su *tražili* novo zaposlenje. (They were looking for a new job.)
3. Ona će *tražiti* novi posao. (She will be looking for a new job.)
4. Oni su *tražili* pomoć od strane vlade. (They were looking for help from the government.)
5. Mi ćemo *tražiti* odgovore. (We will be looking for answers.)